=======
    "## Step 2 — Aggregating with `agg()`\n",
    "\n",
    "### What is `agg()`?\n",
    "\n",
    "`agg()` lets you run **multiple functions at the same time** on a grouped column.\n",
    "\n",
    "Instead of writing:\n",
    "```python\n",
    "reviews.groupby('country').price.min()\n",
    "reviews.groupby('country').price.max()\n",
    "reviews.groupby('country').price.count()\n",
    "```\n",
    "You do it all in one line."
